msgstr "*到那裡：* 更多 &gt; 工具 &gt; 讀者與流通 &gt; 匯入讀者"

#: ../../source/tools.rst:222
msgid "The patron import tool can be used at any time to add patrons in bulk. It is commonly used in universities and schools when a new batch of students registers."
msgstr "任何時間都可以使用讀者匯入工具批次新增讀者。通常用於各級學校新生入學時。"

#: ../../source/tools.rst:229
msgid "Creating a patron import file"
msgstr "新增讀者匯入檔"

#: ../../source/tools.rst:231
msgid "You can download a blank CSV file with a header from the start page of the patron import tool that you can use as a template for your patron import. The header contains all fields that can be used with the patron import tool. You can delete fields and columns you don't need with the exception of a few mandatory ones."
msgstr "您可從讀者匯入工具的啟始頁使用匯入的模板，下載含標頭的空白 CSV 檔案。標頭包括讀者匯入工具的所有欄位。保留必備欄位後，您可刪除不需要的欄位及欄。"

#: ../../source/tools.rst:239
msgid "cardnumber, surname, and all fields you have defined in the :ref:`BorrowerMandatoryField` preference are required and must match valid entries in your database."
msgstr "cardnumber、surname 及定"

#: ../../source/tools.rst:246
msgid "The 'password' should be stored in plaintext, and will be converted to a Bcrypt hash."
msgstr "此 'password' 欄的值必須是純文字，將以 MD5 雜湊演算法編碼。"

#: ../../source/tools.rst:249
msgid "If your passwords are already encrypted, talk to your systems administrator about options"
msgstr "若密碼已經編碼，請洽系統管理員，詢求其他選項"

#: ../../source/tools.rst:254
msgid "Date formats should match your :ref:`system preference <dateformat-label>`, and must be zero-padded, e.g. '01/02/2008'. Alternatively you can supply dates in ISO format (e.g. '2008-12-01')."
msgstr "日期格式必須符合 :ref:`系統偏好 <dateformat-label>` 的設定，且必須補零，如：'01/02/2008'。也可以使用 ISO 格式 (如，'2008-12-01')。"

#: ../../source/tools.rst:260
msgid "If your data contains special characters or diacritics, make sure your file is encoded in UTF-8. Otherwise, the special characters will not be imported correctly."
msgstr ""

